quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,64,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo non e neene-gooto makko on Yuusufa oya tuma? Mi hoolino on e fii on …óon, fodu…óon lam reenugol mo, on hunnaali ahdi. Hoolaare alanaa on ka an wonnde on reenay mo, ko Alla mi hoolori; ko Kanko woni mo∆¥∆¥o reenoowo on mo O yi…ói reenude, …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude yurmetee…ìe …ìen, wonannde mo O yi…ói yurmeede."
  12,65,"Nde …ìe udditunoo do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe √±aametee …óen …óe …ìe addori, …ìe tawi coggeeli mun …óin ruttitaama e ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'ani ben ma…ì…ìe: E ko men …óa…ì…ìata …ìuri ngal teddungal …óoo? ∆äum …óoo ko coggu √±aametee amen on, laam…óo on jonnitirii men …óum teddingol men. Men addanay yim…ìe amen …ìen √±aametee, men reena musi…ó…óo amen on e ko hulan-…óaa mo kon, men …ìeydora …ìetu ngelooba tawde mba ronndannto men; …ìeydorgol …ìetu ngelooba, ko huunde newiinde ka laam…óo on."
  12,66,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: Mi immindintaa mo e moo…óon haa ∆¥ettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde pellet on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara maayde hu…ìindi on fow mon, hara alah heddii…óo e mon, on ronku feere ha…óugol …óum. ∆Åaawo …ìe ∆¥ettanii mo ahdi Alla fellintinaandi e …óum ndin, o maaki: Alla ko seedii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon, seedee Makko on yonii en."
  12,67,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe hino wasiyoo …ìe: wata on naatiroy Misra e damal gootal hi…óon wonndi, ko yo on naatir e dame seertu…óe. Ko …óum …ìurata hisinnde on diini go…ó…óo huu…ìitirta on lorra si o immanike on. Mi alaa wowlirannde on …óum, fii du√±angol on lorra mo Alla faandorii on, wanaa kadi fii poo…óangol on nafa mo Alla yi…óanaa on. √ëaawoore alaa si wanaa √±aawoore Alla nden, fiyaaku alaa si wanaa fiyaaku Makko on. Ko e Makko fawii-mi e kala fiyaaku am, ko e Makko Kanko tun, yo fawo fawotoo…ìe …ìen e fiyakuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  12,68,"∆Åe yahdi e neene-gooto oya on. Nde …ìe naatirnoo e dame seertu…óe, wano ben ma…ì…ìe yamirnoo…ìe non, …óum wonaano hino du√±ana …ìe huunde e ko Alla muuyani …ìe kon. ∆äum ko annde Yaaquuba tun fii …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen o fe√±√±ini, o wasiyii …ìe …óum e hoore himo anndi √±aawoore alaa si wanaa √±aawoore Alla nden. Ko o anndu…óo ko men anndini mo kon e gom…óingol hoddiraaji e jogitagol sabuuji …óin. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe anndaa …óum."
  12,69,"Nde …ìe baaba-gootoo…ìe Yuusufa …ìen naatunoo ka makko hi…ìe wonndi e neene-gooto makko on, o …ìanniti neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maakini mo sirru: ko min woni neene-gooto maa on Yuusuf. wata a sunor piiji kaanu…ói …ói musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen huuwaynoo, immorde lorra e ngayngu hoore-men, e ko …ìe werlii lam kon ka woyndu."